high_descs: Go straight to stove, turn right to face sink.
Pick up the knife on the right.
Position self in front of left side of sink, in front of glass and knife.
Place knife in left side of sink on the right side, blade facing you.  Turn on water, turn off water, drain water.  Pick up knife from the sink.
Place knife on sink ledge, in front and slightly to the right of the other knife.
rinse the knife in the left sink
drop the knife at the edge of the sink
anns.task_desc: place a clean knife by the sink

high_descs: Walk forward almost to the wall but stop short of it and turn right and walk to the sink.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that's on the edge of the counter by the sink.
Take a small step to your left.
Wash the knife in the left sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Spin around in a circle for no reason.
Put the knife back from roughly where you got it from.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife on the counter.
